data.description: Home 17 mins from the beach on  1.07 acres. Enjoy sipping coffee on your large front porch. This 3 bedroom 3 bath has all bedrooms upstairs. Formal dining space when you enter the home to the left. Kitchen in the rear of the house with a window overlooking the back yard and cement slab that you could decorate with outdoor furniture and dining. Large family room, 2 car garage brand new water softener and lots of space to spread out and enjoy. Come see this for yourself!
